2022-04-12 Dorian Lance Yeager <chibby.bromanson@eightbitmonster.com>
	Initial release
2022-04-13 Dorian Lance Yeager <chibby.bromanson@eightbitmonster.com>
  Altering the way tags are displayed.  Now they appear after the path as
	tags:{tagOne tagTwo tagThree}.  This is so you can more easily remove them
	downstream with sed -E 's/ tags:\{.*//

	Improved error handling.  The command will error out if a file does not
	exist.
